===Install===
1. Upload the files to your web server.
2. Download the Yii PHP framework from http://www.yiiframework.com/
3. Extact Yii to a location on your server.
4. Open index.php and set the $yii variable to the location of the Yii framework folder.
5. Create a database from the image in the database file
6. Set the MySQL config settings in /protected/config/main.php
7. Set a cron job on your server to run crawl.php, here is an example cron command that can be used in cPanel: /home/lectopia/public_html/crawl.php, I suggest you run it on a 1 or 2 minute interval.

